        (Map<String, InvoiceBundle>) jobCtx.get("invoiceBundles");

if (bundleMap == null) {
    bundleMap = new HashMap<>();
    jobCtx.put("invoiceBundles", bundleMap);
}
```

### b) After successful `extract(...)` for XML, register bundle

